File: cmd-args-invalid
Scenario: Invalid command line arguments
    [Arguments]     @{args}
    Given a test environment with a valid config
    When we call the application with an invalid command line       ${args}
    Then the call should fail with return code  1
    and stderr contains    unrecognised option
    and the usage information should be printed to stdout

File: cmd-args-invalid-no-config
Scenario: Invalid command line arguments and no configuration file
    [Arguments]     @{args}
    Given a test environment with no config
    When we call the application with an invalid command line       ${args}
    Then the call should fail with return code  1
    and stderr contains    unrecognised option
    and the usage information should be printed to stdout
